des: string
The basic information of the Alliance shows here.
Here are the features of the Alliance. Tap on each feature to view more information.
You may view the Settings and info of the Alliance here; such as alliance members; rankings; etc.
Tap to raise the level of the HQ.\nRaising the level of HQ may improve your combat power.
Here shows the Premium Mines you could search. Go get 'em!

Here is a record of the number of actions you can take in the Dimensional Mine in a single day. Please use them wisely.\nGarrison in the Mines to earn points. The higher the points; the more likely to find rare Mine tiles.
Commander; you may view the Mines you've conquered here. Please claim the final rewards before taking any new actions.
Now; you may choose a Mine to attack. Good luck; commander!
Tap to raise the level of the HQ.\nRaising the level of HQ may improve your combat power.

Upgrading the hero level can improve the attributes.
The War value increases the unit attack.
The Defense value increases the unit HP.
The Command value increases the march size.
Adjust components for each type of units; which give them different effects.

npcContent: Insert it in the Army slot; increase Army's HP!

des: Slide left and right to view and select different types of Alliance Droids
The difficulty of the Alliance Droid increases with the level.
Higher level grants better rewards. Note: Each type of Droid provides slightly different types of rewards.

para: Ocean Area Unlocked|You need to clean up debris in the ocean so that you can build Docks; train naval units; and place overwater decors there.
New Ocean Area Unlocked|The South Island is surrounded by a delightful deep blue shine. You can place certain decors there; but you can't place naval units.

des: Complete radar missions to earn radar EXP and increase radar level
There's a chance to improve the signal by 1 bar upon completing each radar task; and when reaching 5-bar; there will be a 5 star mission
1 click adds 1 bar. Free to improve for the first time everyday
Tap Challenge to set your formation and fight against the Army Boss
You have opportunity to get the following rewards regardless of the battle result.
Here the battle records and Warzone ranking details are shown
Here you can set up your defensive formation and view battle records
Tap the chest to view what's in it
Crafting components require a variety of materials; which may be obtained via Expedition or other activities.
With all the necessary materials; you may start crafting components.
Adjust components for each type of units; which give them different effects.

npcContent: Insert it in the Army slot; increase Army's HP!
